  <p>Drupal's editorial experience has improved considerably over the past several realeases, and Drupal 8 promises to be even better. However, it's still easy for writers and editors to collide with each other when they collaborate. If two people edit the same piece of content at the same time, one user's changes are inevitably lost. Fortunately, the <a href="http://drupal.org/project/content_lock">Content Locking</a> module is ready to help.</p>
